Available Tools: send_email | compose_draft | send_reply | forward_email
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "to": ["string"], "cc": ["string"], "subject": "string", "body": "string", "attachments": ["string"] }
Response Schema: { "message_id": "string", "status": "sent|draft|failed", "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: Email the quarterly budget forecast to the finance committee.
Call: { "func_call": "send_email", "to": ["budget@financegroup.org", "cfo@financegroup.org"], "cc": ["auditor@financegroup.org"], "subject": "Q4 Budget Forecast - Final Draft", "body": "Committee,\n\nPlease review the attached Q4 budget forecast. We need approval by Thursday to proceed with allocations.\n\nRegards,\nSarah Jenkins", "attachments": ["q4_budget_forecast.xlsx"] }
Response: { "message_id": "msg_10293x", "status": "sent", "timestamp": "2023-11-02T09:15:00Z" }

Question: Create a draft asking the catering company about menu options for the retreat.
Call: { "func_call": "compose_draft", "to": ["events@tastybites.com"], "cc": [], "subject": "Inquiry: Menu Options for Annual Retreat", "body": "Hello,\n\nWe are planning our annual retreat for 50 people in November. Could you send over your vegetarian and gluten-free menu options?\n\nThanks,\nEvent Coordinator", "attachments": [] }
Response: { "message_id": "draft_20485y", "status": "draft", "timestamp": "2023-11-02T10:30:22Z" }

Question: Reply to the recruiter confirming interest in the interview slot.
Call: { "func_call": "send_reply", "to": ["hiring@techstart.io"], "cc": [], "subject": "Re: Interview Scheduling - Software Engineer Role", "body": "Hi,\n\nThank you for reaching out. Tuesday at 10 AM works perfectly for me. I look forward to speaking with the team.\n\nBest,\nJordan Lee", "attachments": [] }
Response: { "message_id": "msg_30576z", "status": "sent", "timestamp": "2023-11-02T11:45:10Z" }

Question: Forward the security audit results to the CISO.
Call: { "func_call": "forward_email", "to": ["ciso@securenet.com"], "cc": ["it-director@securenet.com"], "subject": "Fwd: Security Audit Results - November", "body": "Team,\n\nForwarding the latest security audit results. Please note the critical findings on page 12 that require immediate attention.\n\nRegards,\nSecurity Analyst", "attachments": ["security_audit_nov.pdf"] }
Response: { "message_id": "msg_40667a", "status": "sent", "timestamp": "2023-11-02T13:20:45Z" }

